## 1. Project Overview

**LabProject** is a production-grade, multi-branch clinical lab management system. It manages the full test lifecycle — from order intake and sample tracking through result verification and patient-facing PDF delivery — while providing operational dashboards, configurable reporting, and a white-label AI insights engine.

The system is designed for single or multi-branch lab setups and accommodates international locale and RTL layout requirements. It serves five distinct user roles: lab admins, clinicians, referring doctors, patients, and finance teams — each with tailored views, permissions, and communication channels.

