## 2. My Role & Contributions

### 📊 Analytics Visualization Governance
Standardized color semantics across Chart.js and Flot chart libraries. Introduced default and module-aware palettes (Reports, Accounting, Appointments) with consistent status color mapping and an admin-facing Charts configuration UI — enabling palette changes without engineering involvement.

### 🤖 Smart AI Engine Operationalization
Designed the compliance-first, white-label AI layer: provider/model governance, cost caps, failover sequencing, consent logging, and mandatory non-diagnostic disclaimers on all patient-facing outputs.

### 📅 Scheduling & Resource Integrity
Built resource-aware appointment booking with branch-level conflict prevention, setup/cleanup time buffers, ICS export endpoints (patient and admin), and optional Google/Microsoft calendar sync with read-only import support.

### 💰 Doctor Commission Wallet
Implemented configurable referral rules, credit/debit ledgers, payout request workflows, and webhook-triggered credits tied to confirmed payment events — giving referring doctors real-time financial transparency.

