## 3. Platform Architecture

**Core modules and their data flows:**

```
Clinical Operations
├── Test orders → Sample lifecycle → Results entry → Verification → Release
├── Microbiology: cultures, antibiotic panels, sensitivity mapping
└── PDF reports: configurable layouts (fonts, margins, accent colors, headers)

Scheduling
├── Branch-specific resource booking with conflict detection
├── Setup/cleanup buffer windows
└── ICS export (patient & admin) + Google/Microsoft calendar sync

Financials
├── Group-based invoicing & receipts
├── Expense categories & accounting reports (incl. doctor-centric views)
└── Commission wallet: referral rules → ledger → payout requests → webhook credits

Communications
├── Email (SMTP): patient codes, password reset, receipts, test reports
├── SMS (Twilio): patient codes, test notifications
├── WhatsApp: receipt and report messaging
└── Patient PDFs: branded headers/footers, accent colors, QR portal links

Admin & Governance
├── Theme overlay: brand CSS variables across admin/patient UIs
├── Charts config UI: default and per-module palette overrides
├── Reports settings: margins, fonts, colors, images, alignment
└── Roles & permissions, Google 2FA, API key management
```

