## 4. Smart AI Engine

The platform includes a white-label AI insights engine designed around compliance and clinical authority preservation.

| Capability | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Scope** | Non-diagnostic, patient education only |
| **Disclaimers** | Mandatory on all AI-generated patient-facing content |
| **Consent logging** | Recorded per interaction |
| **Provider governance** | Admin-selectable provider/model via backend UI |
| **Cost controls** | Per-provider cost caps enforced at the infrastructure layer |
| **Failover** | Configurable fallback sequence across providers |
| **Report analysis** | AI summaries and trend insights on external and internal lab reports |
| **Clinical authority** | AI augments, never overrides, clinician-verified results |

> **Design principle:** Provider switching is backend-only. Patient-facing interfaces are fully white-label with no AI branding exposed.

