### 5.1 Monthly Test Volume by Branch
**Chart type:** Grouped bar chart
**Module palette:** Operations (teal)
**Library:** Chart.js

**Context:** Lab administrators need to compare test throughput across branches to allocate staff and resources effectively. This chart lives on the main operations dashboard and updates in real time.

**Design decision:** The module-aware teal palette was chosen to distinguish operations data from accounting (blue) and appointment (amber) data — preventing cross-module visual confusion when multiple charts appear on the same screen.

**Business impact:** Faster identification of branch-level underperformance and capacity gaps.

