### 5.2 Invoice Status Breakdown
**Chart type:** Stacked horizontal bar chart
**Status mapping:** Green (paid) / Amber (partial) / Red (unpaid)
**Library:** Chart.js

**Context:** Finance teams need to prioritize collections activity across patient groups. Each row represents a billing group; segments show the proportion of settled, partial, and overdue invoices.

**Design decision:** Semantic status colors (green/amber/red) were enforced as a platform-wide standard rather than allowing per-chart color choices. This makes status states immediately recognizable regardless of which chart or module the user is viewing.

**Business impact:** Reduced time to identify high-risk billing groups; improved cash flow visibility.

