### 5.3 Result Release Rate (SLA Compliance)
**Chart type:** Donut chart
**Module palette:** Reports (green)
**Library:** Flot

**Context:** Clinical managers monitor the percentage of test results released within the agreed SLA window. This chart appears on the Reports dashboard alongside raw counts.

**Design decision:** The donut format was selected over a simple percentage card because it communicates proportionality at a glance and supports a second segment (delayed releases) without clutter. The Reports module palette (green ramp) differentiates it from Appointments and Accounting charts.

**Business impact:** Early detection of result bottlenecks; supports SLA reporting to hospital partners.

