- 🔴 **Financial transparency** — Real-time commission ledgers with automated webhook-triggered credits improved referring doctor trust and reduced manual payout reconciliation.

- 🟣 **Elevated patient communications** — Brand-aligned PDFs, email, SMS, and WhatsApp notifications — all configurable by non-technical admins — improved readability and reduced patient support queries.

- ⚪ **Compliance posture** — AI-generated content is non-diagnostic, fully white-label, and includes mandatory disclaimers with consent logging on every interaction.

